title: Furnished Eastside Home Available On Short-Term Basis
posting_body: ['Furnished Eastside Home Available On Short-Term Basis', 'Property Address', '616 Austin Avenue | Sonoma, CA 95476', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Sonoma Properties', 'Description', '3bd/2ba Furnished Eastside home available on a short-term basis.', ' This stylish home is just a block away from the Sonoma Plaza.', " Tastefully remodeled and fully furnished, the home features hardwood floors in the main living areas, living room with fireplace, formal dining room, a Chef's kitchen with teak cabinets, stainless steel appliances and two ovens including a Thermador gas range.", 'The rear garden has been professionally landscaped and features a lush lawn, mature trees, an arbor-covered patio, wisteria covered arbor for outdoor dining, deck, small herb garden and a western red cedar hot tub.', ' This rental has A/C, washer and dryer, a 240 volt outlet for charging in driveway and a 1-car garage.', ' Rent includes regular landscaping service, pest control service, bi-monthly hot-tub service, weekly garbage pickup, water, cable and phone.', 'Tenant pays for PG&E.  No pets.', '**Available beginning August 1st, 3 month minimum**', 'For more information, call Sonoma Properties at', 'show contact info', '.', 'BRE License #01931046', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 3BD/2.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,622', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $6,500.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $35.00', 'Security Deposit: $9,750.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats not allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
